    "\n",
    "### 12.1 Summary of Key Findings\n",
    "\n",
    "This project conducted a systematic comparative analysis of three supervised machine learning models Logistic Regression, Random Forest, and Gradient Boosting for predicting hotel reservation cancellations. The analysis followed a structured workflow encompassing dataset justification, exploratory data analysis, preprocessing design, model training with hyperparameter optimization, and multi-dimensional evaluation.\n",
